ml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-1626003738560329v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by explaining", "description": "Follow (us) @Explaining to Learn something NEW every day 🧠💫 \n\nAndy Serkis transformed movie history with his performance as Gollum in The Lord of the Rings. 🧙‍♂️🎭\n\nInstead of just lending his voice, Serkis performed the character physically on set using motion capture, crawling, twisting, and acting alongside the cast so animators could capture every movement and emotion. His split personality, switching between Gollum and Sméagol, brought depth, tragedy, and realism to a fully digital character. 🎥✨\n\nThe role proved that motion capture could be true acting, not just animation, and it changed how films approach digital characters forever.\n\nLet us know your thoughts below!\n\n•\n\n#explore #storytelling #interesting #reels #learn", "duration": 32.8, "timestamp": 1766579400, "uploader_id": "65381444674", "uploader": "Explaining", "channel": "explaining", "like_count": 88497, "comment_count": 909, "comments": [{"author": "craigndebs", "author_id": "48412808302", "id": "18090098722930546", "text": "🙌", "timestamp": 1774440825}, {"author": "jammo_9", "author_id": "270299007", "id": "18083814893049526", "text": "That’s me after a particularly good curry 🥴", "timestamp": 1774311303}, {"author": "sidiousart", "author_id": "7962064023", "id": "17941346445149985", "text": "Wow!!! ❤️", "timestamp": 1774213023}, {"author": "77mdaaa", "author_id": "48754823729", "id": "17852171676689347", "text": "No Oscar for this btw", "timestamp": 1774209147}, {"author": "diniszzz7", "author_id": "8782072603", "id": "18103180675902572", "text": "Monkey from Odyssey to the West", "timestamp": 1774191110}, {"author": "jacksonmaclellan", "author_id": "80431530233", "id": "18412759675131893", "text": "This guy is good. He should be an actor", "timestamp": 1774153523}, {"author": "raylop285", "author_id": "72099750294", "id": "17876400483546268", "text": "This is precious", "timestamp": 1773711537}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/605304106_1361903361799144_3925085072986773756_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEMFIfZv5ailDh-HE4BDQoYNYGUjHRT-DehKn4hQeGqa7ayHT-ZWpQK_l8Xkzvph40&_nc_ohc=Yh4GNf5FSfUQ7kNvwFptdot&_nc_gid=XtLevI8MRPIAvdX-Uk7tGg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af2GUKzUG8_0okVQBT9bXa40sCyGVvfHeumPcBlUIAbdXw&oe=69D4DCF6&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/605304106_1361903361799144_3925085072986773756_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEMFIfZv5ailDh-HE4BDQoYNYGUjHRT-DehKn4hQeGqa7ayHT-ZWpQK_l8Xkzvph40&_nc_ohc=Yh4GNf5FSfUQ7kNvwFptdot&_nc_gid=XtLevI8MRPIAvdX-Uk7tGg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af2GUKzUG8_0okVQBT9bXa40sCyGVvfHeumPcBlUIAbdXw&oe=69D4DCF6&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/605304106_1361903361799144_3925085072986773756_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEMFIfZv5ailDh-HE4BDQoYNYGUjHRT-DehKn4hQeGqa7ayHT-ZWpQK_l8Xkzvph40&_nc_ohc=Yh4GNf5FSfUQ7kNvwFptdot&_nc_gid=XtLevI8MRPIAvdX-Uk7tGg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af2GUKzUG8_0okVQBT9bXa40sCyGVvfHeumPcBlUIAbdXw&oe=69D4DCF6&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 1080, "height": 1917, "id": "2", "resolution": "